# The repo-level Minos/.gitignore ignores `results/` and `*.png` everywhere. future/ is a
# tracked, quarantined build, so re-include its committed results/figures here, while still
# keeping the reproducible binary cohort caches (regenerated by data.py) out of git.
# The built manuscript (paper/minos.pdf) is tracked deliberately; LaTeX intermediates are not.
!results/
!figures/
results/cohorts/
*.npz
paper/*.aux
paper/*.log
paper/*.out
